text: Mörel-Filet is a municipality of the district of Raron in the canton of Valais in Switzerland. On 1 January 2009, the former municipalities of Filet and Mörel merged into the new municipality of Mörel-Filet. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:2009 establishments in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Raron
